data.title: Memorial service for Lydia Shum Din
data.meta_description: A photo of Hong Kong comedian actress Lydia Shum Din-Ha is displayed during a memorial service at the Coliseum in Hong Kong, South China, March 2, 2008.
data.text:
Memorial service for Lydia Shum Din-Ha

(Xinhua)

Updated: 2008-03-04 09:31

Joyce Cheng Yan-yee (R), daughter of late Hong Kong comedian actress Lydia Shum Din-Ha, and Adam Cheng Siu Chau, ex-husband of Shum, attend a memorial service at the Coliseum in Hong Kong, China, March 2, 2008. [Xinhua]
